trans-unit.source: Provides data for the known, but unreferenced, object found in an encoded SOAP XML stream during deserialization.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o objeto conhecido, mas não referenciado, encontrado em um fluxo XML de SOAP codificado durante a desserialização.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.UnreferencedObjectEventArgs> class, see the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> event of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.UnreferencedObjectEventArgs> de classe, consulte o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> evento o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> event occurs only when you call the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.Deserialize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> evento ocorre somente quando você chama o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.Deserialize%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling events, see [Events Overview](~/docs/framework/winforms/events-overview-windows-forms.md)
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre a manipulação de eventos, consulte [visão geral sobre eventos](~/docs/framework/winforms/events-overview-windows-forms.md)
